{"id": 2869, "genre": 1004, "title": "如果亲临案发现场，你会是哪种类型的侦探？", "description": "真相，永远只有一个。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive ）", "record_count": 11922, "comment_count": 166, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190328191049Do6OwBxEVe7jqHlA.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 6, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-04T17:00:03Z", "column": null, "normal_questions": [{"id": 5600, "content": "发生命案，你的第一反应是：", "image": "img/question/question/20190328154345McOfDyBvlRTqeVwk.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336177, "title": "回忆命案周边环境 ", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336179, "title": "检查尸体", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336180, "title": "看时间", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336184, "title": "找警察问话", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5601, "content": "询问目击者的时候，你会更在意：", "image": "img/question/question/20190328191731vydb68nujUKT1COR.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336185, "title": "他的肢体细节", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336186, "title": "说的内容", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336187, "title": "语气", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336188, "title": "有没有不在场证明", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5602, "content": "你在墙上发现一块红黑色血迹，你会：", "image": "img/question/question/20190328183603d0DaIqGBbwHoENyv.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336189, "title": "闻一闻，并记下血迹的形状", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336190, "title": "问问助手怎么看", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336191, "title": "观察血迹与周围环境的关系", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336192, "title": "有点晕血", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5604, "content": "你在地上捡起一片纸张碎片，直觉告诉你：", "image": "img/question/question/20190328184308dtCmiXNzpcg1R0Jy.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336194, "title": "这和凶手有关", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336195, "title": "这是死者生前留下的证据", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336196, "title": "这是有人为警方留下的线索", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336197, "title": "先用火烤烤试试", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5605, "content": "这时，隔壁房间突然传来一阵尖叫，你会认为：", "image": "img/question/question/20190328185022oAHNPQiFTj5XC9Sp.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336199, "title": "ta看到了凶手", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336200, "title": "ta发现了新尸体", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336201, "title": "不好！ta有危险", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336202, "title": "ta看到蟑螂了", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5606, "content": "死者的家属在现场哭嚎，你会：", "image": "img/question/question/20190328184932D1NVpRgFTXz8WHnb.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336203, "title": "静静观察", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336204, "title": "同情，但希望ta不要妨碍工作", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336205, "title": "安慰ta", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336206, "title": "躲ta远一点", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5607, "content": "梳理案情时，你最可能做什么：\r\n", "image": "img/question/question/20190328185410OoPcKHn5qvf4BS6e.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336207, "title": "闭着眼睛思考", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336208, "title": "把所有线索记在本子上", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336209, "title": "灵光闪现", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336210, "title": "使劲挠头发", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5608, "content": "今天在现场没有什么收获，你计划回去第一件事是：", "image": "img/question/question/201903281858370ykR7oKSPQcEDwYf.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336211, "title": "在自己的世界里迷失一会儿", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336212, "title": "处理和案子有关文件", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336213, "title": "求助特定领域的专家", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336214, "title": "在沙发上瘫着休息", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5609, "content": "你推断出某个人嫌疑最大，但没有直接证据，你会：", "image": "img/question/question/201903281900473n9B6xLmUN2qXAeD.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 336216, "title": "单独跟ta对峙", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336217, "title": "跟踪ta", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336218, "title": "设计陷阱让ta露出马脚", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 336220, "title": "直接召集警方，揭发ta", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 